Package courses

Class Session

java.lang.Object
courses.Session
public class Session
extends java.lang.Object
This class represesnts a session for a course. It contains a max number of students allowed to join the session, minimum number of students for each session. It also contains a teacher for the session along with the list of students.
Since:
: 12/02/2020
